Class CsvInvoicesReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.konik.csv.mapper.CsvInvoicesReader

  • public class CsvInvoicesReader

    Reader class used for reading CSV files and returning a List of Invoices.

    This is high-level component that should be used to import invoices from CSV files.
